headline: Trane Technologies to Present at the J.P. Morgan Industrials Conference
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, February 28, 2025--Trane Technologies plc (NYSE: TT), a global climate innovator, today announced that company leadership will participate in a fireside chat at the J.P. Morgan Industrials Conference. They will speak at 10:30 a.m. EST on Tuesday, March 11, 2025.
